<br>
Basic drop items are 0.5 points<br>
Items for Epics are 0.5-1 point (depending one what and where it came from)<br>
Items Drops from Demi-Gods are 1.0 points<br>
Normal BP drops Hate/Fear/Kael 4.0 points<br>
Normal legging drops are 3.0 points<br>
Rare BP drops are 5-9 points (Jaundiced BP was 5 and Mann robe was 9)<br>
Rare leggs are more expensive (cobalt legs were 4 points)<br>
<br>
